# Anything NOT listed here ends up in the build context — keep this tight.
# Secrets in particular must never enter a layer (.claude/rules/public-repo.md §2).

**/.git
**/.github
**/.gitignore
**/.gitattributes

# Dependencies are reinstalled inside the image from the lockfile.
**/node_modules
**/.pnpm-store

# Build output and caches.
**/dist
**/dist-ssr
**/.vite
**/coverage
**/.nyc_output
**/*.tsbuildinfo

# Secrets — non-negotiable.
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
**/*.pem
**/*.key

# Editor / OS noise.
**/.vscode
**/.idea
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db

# Docs / meta — image doesn't need them at runtime.
**/README.md
**/CONTRIBUTING.md
**/CHANGELOG.md
**/LICENSE
**/CLAUDE.md
**/.claude
**/renovate.json5
**/lefthook.yml
**/commitlint.config.mjs
**/biome.json

# Compose files are operator-side, not image-side.
**/compose.yaml
**/compose.dev.yaml
**/Dockerfile
**/.dockerignore
